e the error mentions a missing optional javax.mail, I'll consider adding `javax.mail:mail:1.4.7` and maybe `javax.activation` if it’s not already included. I should also check the availability in m2.\"}]}"}, {"type": "toolCall", "id": "call_HxgznKrTjnbGIM2I0Spdyp4E|fc_070345f6deca852e0169fece91cd78819583306150d46654fa", "name": "bash", "arguments": {"command": "find ~/.m2/repository ~/.gradle/caches/modules-2/files-2.1 -path '*javax.mail*mail*jar' -o -path '*com.sun.mail*javax.mail*jar' 2>/dev/null | head -20"}}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 2296, "output": 756, "cacheRead": 89600, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 92652, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "toolUse", "timestamp": 1778306691515, "responseId": "resp_070345f6deca852e0169fece8444948195a2a8242c624f859a"}}
